        {
            "title": "白宮國家經濟委員會主任哈塞特支持聯儲會降息 稱這是一個審慎的選擇",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 白宮國家經濟委員會主任凱文·哈塞特對<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:聯儲會;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/聯儲會\">聯儲會</a>降息25個基點的決定表示支持，儘管此前總統唐納德·川普及其盟友曾敦促採取更大降息幅度。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">哈塞特周四上午接受CNBC採訪時表示，「聯儲會審視所有模型、聽取多元意見後作出決策，在當前經濟看似將加速成長、通膨雖放緩但仍高於目標值的背景下，這種做法更為審慎。我認為此次決策實現了折中平衡，這可能是相當審慎的選擇。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此番言論發表於聯儲會政策制定者一年來首次降息的次日。主席傑羅姆·鮑威爾指出風險平衡已發生變化，並引述近期數據中顯現的「就業成長大幅放緩及其他勞動力市場疲軟跡象」作為依據。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-bd4f1014-f25a-37c8-8aec-c3278a15bb83-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次決議中出現一張反對票，由斯蒂芬·米蘭投出。這位周二剛加入聯儲會理事會的理事此前擔任川普政府白宮首席經濟學家。米蘭主張降息50個基點，但鮑威爾表示「如此幅度的降息根本沒有獲得廣泛支持」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">哈塞特表示，「我知曉同事斯蒂芬主張降息50個基點，但我認為25個基點是相當廣泛的共識。我認為這是朝著大幅降低利率方向邁出的良好第一步。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Hassett Offers Endorsement of Fed Rate Cut, Says It’s a Start</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%99%BD%E5%AE%AE%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%A7%94%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%BB%E5%93%88%E5%A1%9E%E7%89%B9%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF-%E7%A8%B1%E9%80%99%E6%98%AF-%E5%80%8B%E5%AF%A9%E6%85%8E%E7%9A%84%E9%81%B8%E6%93%87-133122234.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-18 23:10:44",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "高盛首席美國股票策略師David Kostin將於年內退休",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"David Kostin\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/APXcejslVmCM8V_Hrb0raw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/b76208eb06e3a146eab6e6a269dbae46\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">David Kostin</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 高盛集團首席美國股票策略師David Kostin在這家投資銀行工作了三十多年後將在年底退休。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他1994年加入高盛，後在2004年進入投資組合策略團隊。彭博新聞看到的備忘錄顯示，其職位將由Ben Snider接手 。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"大衛·科斯汀攝影師：Victor J. Blue/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/HVUzCgE2oiUT6GKDskbjBg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/215355546d8b5ca43b36843f2bbbe6a9\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">大衛·科斯汀攝影師：Victor J. Blue/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「很榮幸能擔任這個職位，」 Kostin在接受採訪時說，「這家銀行的文化節奏非常快，你共事的很多是傑出的人。標準非常高，而市場瞬息萬變。但在華爾街干了40年的分析師後，現在對我來說是個退休的好時機。」</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-12399b2b-4434-34a6-b1ad-701abd26b4d9-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Kostin「為股票市場分析帶來了以客戶為中心的做法，制定了嚴謹的框架，並提供了差異化的產品和真知灼見」， 高盛首席經濟學家Jan Hatzius在另一份備忘錄中寫道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高盛發言人證實了這兩份備忘錄的內容。彭博也聯繫了Snider徵求意見。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Top Goldman US Stock Strategist David Kostin to Retire This Year</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%AB%98%E7%9B%9B%E9%A6%96%E5%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%82%A1%E7%A5%A8%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5%E5%B8%ABdavid-kostin%E5%B0%87%E6%96%BC%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%A7%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91-165903380.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-19 01:45:48",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "川普請求最高法院允許他罷免聯儲會理事麗莎·庫克",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 川普請求美國最高法院允許他在案件審理期間罷免聯儲會理事麗莎·庫克，這使得最高法院被正式捲入了有關央行獨立性的爭議。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">司法部周四向最高法院提出請求，要求至少暫時中止聯邦法官允許庫克繼續留任的裁決。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump Asks Supreme Court to Let Him Fire Fed’s LISA Cook</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E8%AB%8B%E6%B1%82%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E5%85%81%E8%A8%B1%E4%BB%96%E7%BD%B7%E5%85%8D%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83%E7%90%86%E4%BA%8B%E9%BA%97%E8%8E%8E-%E5%BA%AB%E5%85%8B-154743950.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-19 01:45:50",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "一掃前周異象 美國初請失業救濟人數創近四年來最大降幅",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國首次申請失業救濟人數錄得近四年來最大減量，扭轉了此前一周異常猛增的勢頭，也符合經濟中裁員水平較低的情況。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">勞工部周四公佈的數據顯示，截至9月13日當周首次申領失業救濟的人數減少了3.3萬至23.1萬。彭博對經濟學家的調查顯示，他們的預測中值為24萬人申請。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">持續申領的人數在前一周下降至192萬。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Initial Jobless Claims Drop by Most in Almost Four Years</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-cd2c6442-c524-3c52-96a2-05d402422733-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Chris Middleton.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8E%83%E5%89%8D%E5%91%A8%E7%95%B0%E8%B1%A1-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%88%9D%E8%AB%8B%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD%E6%95%91%E6%BF%9F%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8%E5%89%B5%E8%BF%91%E5%9B%9B%E5%B9%B4%E4%BE%86%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%8D%E5%B9%85-124120378.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-18 22:00:54",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "減息時代開啟錢何處去？7大資產部署全拆解｜財經百科(更新)",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"美聯儲今年內首度減息0.25厘，且多數官員預期今年內還將進行兩次減息。圖為聯儲局主席鮑威爾。(AP)\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/HH4SK90sYEaaYUgayivCOg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/tl/am730_578/0dde3e1a2881ecbb9ae913899132aab1\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美聯儲今年內首度減息0.25厘，且多數官員預期今年內還將進行兩次減息。圖為聯儲局主席鮑威爾。(AP)</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span><strong>【9月18日更新】</strong>美國聯儲局在今次會議中一如預期減息0.25厘，而且多數官員預期今年內還將進行兩次減息，預計年底利率區間將降至3.75厘至3.50厘水平。此次降息不僅是美聯儲</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>今年以來首次利率調整，更標誌著美國貨幣政策很可能正式轉向寬鬆周期。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>在全新的貨幣政策環境下，作為投資者，如何在減息潮中部署資金，才能把握機遇、實現階級超越和資產增值？本文將為你逐一拆解。</span></span></span></span></span></p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">中原城市領先指數：樓價逐步回升</h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>在香港這個國際金融中心，房地產長期被視為最穩健且具備可靠長線回報的投資選擇之一。儘管低息環境的持續性仍存在不確定性，但美國正式開啟減息周期，意味著借貸成本將有可能逐步下降，對樓市構成實質利好。</span></span></span></span></span></p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-180c1860-ea19-3168-9ca5-b51ca7e33da3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據中原城市領先指數(CCL)，香港樓價自2021年高位約190點回落至136點，目前逐步回升至138.7點。政府已將400萬元以下物業的印花稅大幅降至100元。雖然高息環境曾壓抑樓市，但隨著美國進入減息周期，資金不排除大舉流入樓市。金管局總裁余偉文指出，<span><span><span>美國減息利好香港經濟和樓市，看見本港今年經濟慢慢向好。</span></span></span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>買樓相比其他投資的獨特優勢，在於它兼具<strong>「居住、收租、升值」</strong>三重效益，包括：</span></span></span></span></span></p><ol class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-decimal\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span><strong>居住需求</strong>：提供實際居住價值，毋須擔心租金波動或業主收樓</span></span></span></span></span></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-decimal\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span><strong>租金回報</strong>：在低息環境下，租金回報率相對吸引，可產生被動收入</span></span></span></span></span></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-decimal\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span><strong>物業升值</strong>：長期來看，香港土地稀缺，優質物業抗通脹能力強，加上地價上升，過往不少買家正是透過物業升值累積財富</span></span></span></span></span></p></li></ol><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>目前香港住宅物業的租金回報率普遍維持在2%至4%左右，若投資者能發掘5%以上回報的物業，確實具備較強的投資吸引力。</span></span></span></span></span></p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>買美債財息兼收？</span></span></span></span></span></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國國債一直被全球投資者視為穩健資產，具備資本保值和穩定收息的雙重優勢。目前，在美債息已開始回落<span><span><span><span><span>，截至發稿：</span></span></span></span></span></p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong><span><span><span><span><span>2</span><span>年期美債：收益率約3.53%</span></span></span></span></span></strong></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong><span><span><span><span><span>10</span><span>年期美債：收益率約4.04%</span></span></span></span></span></strong></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong><span><span><span><span><span>20</span><span>年期美債：收益率逼近4.62%</span></span></span></span></span></strong></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong><span><span><span><span><span>30</span><span>年期美債：收益率一度超過4.65%</span></span></span></span></span></strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這為投資者提供了鎖定高息的機會。隨著聯儲局進入減息周期，投資美債或將迎來「債息+價差」的收益。若不想持有美債太長時間，可考慮相關股票，如IEF美債7至10年ETF和TLT等。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>股票投資：捕捉增長機會的關鍵策略</span></span></span></span></span></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">除了投資物業和債券外，美股市場一直是全球投資者的焦點，特別是「美股七雄」及標普500指數成分股。<span><span><span><span><span>若不想單押個股，</span></span></span></span></span>考慮指數型ETF，以分散風險並享受市場增長：</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><strong><span>DIA</span></strong><span><strong>：</strong>追蹤道瓊斯工業指數，屬穩健股市</span></span></span></span></span></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><strong><span>QQQ</span></strong><span><strong>：</strong>追蹤納斯達克100指數，以科技股為主，增長潛力高</span></span></span></span></span></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><strong><span>VOO/SPY</span></strong><span><strong>：</strong>追蹤標普500指數，屬均衡配置，長期回報穩定</span></span></span></span></span></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><strong><span>BRK.B</span></strong><span><strong>：</strong>「股神」巴菲特旗艦之一，長期錄得升幅</span></span></span></span></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">至於港股，雖然近年表現波動，但近期升勢回暖。若對個股選擇缺乏信心，盈富基金(2800)可作為理想的被動投資工具。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>高息股：波動市場中的避風港</span></span></span></span></span></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在動盪市況中，高息股以穩定派息特性成為精明投資者的核心配置。這類股票不僅提供持續現金流，還能在股價下跌時創造更高收益率，實現「跌市賺息，升市賺價」的雙重優勢。其投資要點包括：</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span><strong>派息穩定性：</strong>重點關注連續5年以上維持或增加派息的企業</span></span></span></span></span></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span><strong>行業特性：</strong>公用事業、電訊、房地產信託(REITs)通常派息較穩定</span></span></span></span></span></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span><strong>估值合理性：</strong>避免「高息陷阱」，需確認股息率可持續</span></span></span></span></span></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span><strong>分散配置：</strong>構建含5至10隻高息股的投資組合，降低單一股票風險</span></span></span></span></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span><a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:《am730》曾經精選10隻高息港股;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93/%E9%AB%98%E6%81%AF%E8%82%A12025-10%E9%9A%BB%E6%B8%AF%E8%82%A1%E5%85%A8%E8%B7%91%E5%87%BA-6%E9%9A%BB%E5%8D%B3%E5%B0%87%E9%99%A4%E6%B7%A8%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E6%B4%BE8%E5%8E%98-%E6%81%92%E7%94%9F%E5%A2%9E%E6%B4%BE%E6%81%AF8-5%E6%9C%8821%E6%97%A5%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0-/388877\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">《am730》曾經精選10隻高息港股</a></span><span>，這些企業不僅具備優異派息紀錄，最高超過8厘，更能助您在市場風浪中穩守收益。</span></span></span></span></span></p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>細價股：爆升10倍的尋寶藝術</span></span></span></span></span></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">細價股對於經驗豐富的投資者來說，勢必帶來可觀回報，但需要專業分析能力。關鍵在於深入分析財務，特別是公司的資產負債表，並關注業務轉型或行業復甦的契機。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這些公司往往因特定因素在IPO後股價被不合理地壓低，但若基礎穩健或業務持續發展，實現「均值回歸」後的回報可能超乎想像。加上，若大股東願意派息，除了可派發70至100厘的股息外，還可能面臨收購、私有化或「賣殼」的機會，使細價股極具吸引力。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>黃金投資：亂世中的避險王者</span></span></span></span></span></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在當前國際地緣政治局勢持續動盪的環境下，黃金作為傳統終極避險資產，價格持續走強。現貨金價目前已穩定站穩每盎司3,700美元關口，年內累計漲幅接近四成，表現甚至超越同期比特幣等數字資產。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著全球多地地緣政治風險升溫，市場避險情緒持續高漲，推動資金大量流入黃金市場。分析指出，在國際局勢不確定性加劇的背景下，黃金作為具有保值功能的硬資產，成為避險資金的首選配置標的。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:如何投資黃金？買實金？還是黃金ETF？;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/column/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91-%E8%B2%B7%E5%AF%A6%E9%87%91-%E9%82%84%E6%98%AF%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91etf-/599826\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">如何投資黃金？買實金？還是黃金ETF？</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:金價屢破新高 增持是否太遲;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/column/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E9%87%91%E5%83%B9%E5%B1%A2%E7%A0%B4%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-%E5%A2%9E%E6%8C%81%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%A4%AA%E9%81%B2/598346\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">金價屢破新高 增持是否太遲</a></p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>加密貨幣：最具顛覆性的資產</span></span></span></span></span></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>目前，</span></span></span></span></span>加密貨幣已從邊緣資產躍升為重要的投資選擇。比特幣<span><span><span><span><span>(Bitcoin)</span></span></span></span></span>近期突破10萬美元大關，主要受以下三大因素推動：</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">特朗普政策轉向支持加密貨幣</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">機構投資者持續加碼</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">固有的稀缺特性</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然而，加密貨幣市場如同過山車，雖然比特幣和以太幣相對穩健，但單日暴漲暴跌10%常見，且其他加密貨幣面臨監管風險和安全隱患。因此，若追求穩定收益，債券、黃金或高息股更為適合；但若能承受更高風險，加密貨幣可能成為未來10年最具顛覆性的資產之一。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>(以上資料僅供參考，投資前應考慮個人財政狀況及市場風險。)</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文刊登於 AM730 <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/減息時代開啟錢何處去-7大資產部署全拆解-財經百科-更新-/566684?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/減息時代開啟錢何處去-7大資產部署全拆解-財經百科-更新-/566684?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/減息時代開啟錢何處去-7大資產部署全拆解-財經百科-更新-/566684?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral</a></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%AE%9A%E5%AD%98%E6%B8%9B%E6%81%AF%E6%BD%AE%E9%BB%9E%E7%AE%97%E5%A5%BD-%E8%B2%B7%E6%A8%93%E8%B2%B7%E8%82%A1%E7%AD%89%E8%B3%87%E7%94%A2%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2-%E6%96%87%E7%9D%87%E6%B8%85-%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E7%99%BE%E7%A7%91-102200259.html",
